<h3>Zombie Rush</h3>
This is my portfolio piece, a solo project developed during my third year at University.
It is a top-down, wave based zombie shooter game. To see my development process, please see my development log
<a href="https://zakstanyer.wixsite.com/zakstanyer/zombierush" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: underline; padding: 1px"> here.</a>
<br><br>
<p>This is my final solo project, developed during my third year at University.
It is a top-down shooter featuring upgrade trees, an inventory system,
saving and loading progress, and more.</p>
<br>
